data.description: The moment you step inside of this ground level, corner situated home of this gated community you will feel just that - at home - as you are embraced by the inviting open layout overflowing with natural lighting provided by the large windows throughout the home! This is main level living at its finest with endless luxuries! The living room features high ceilings and a gas fireplace which provides for a fabulous room to gather in. The kitchen is complete with solid countertops a gorgeous backsplash, pantry, ample cupboard storage space, AND comes fully equipped with a dishwasher, refrigerator, stovetop/oven, and microwave! The dining room showcases a large window that expands the wall to enjoy views of outside, and the dining room walks out to the private covered patio so that you may enjoy the great outdoors from the comforts of your own home. This home has its own laundry area, and the washer and dryer are included in the purchase price! The primary bedroom has its own full attached bathroom and walk-in closet. The home has a second room which can be utilized as another bedroom or for office space, exercise room, area to enjoy hobbies, and/or more; and it has access to the full second bathroom. Beautiful vinyl flooring expand throughout the home with tiled bathrooms. The community clubhouse is fully equipped with a pool, hot tub, work out facility, TV and gathering room and kitchenette. Air Conditioning is already installed. Live nearby to parks, schools, shopping, restaurants, and other amenities which add to the splendor of this home!
